  "prob_desc_output_spec": "Print \"YES\" without quotes if a potion with efficiency exactly k can be bought in the store and \"NO\" without quotes otherwise. You can output each of the letters in any register.",
  "source_code": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nint main()\n{\n\tdouble l,r,x,y,k,i;\n\tscanf(\"%lf%lf%lf%lf%lf\",&l,&r,&x,&y,&k);\n\t\n\tfor(i= x; i<=y ; i++)\n\t{\n\t\tdouble val = 0;\n\t\tval = i*k;\n\t\tif(val>=l && val<=r)\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tprintf(\"YES\\n\");\n\t\t\treturn 0;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\t\tprintf(\"NO\\n\");\n\t\treturn 0;\n}\n",
